2  Weather

The most common environmental dataset that people encounter is the weather. Every major type of media devotes time to the weather: newspapers, news shows, apps, twitter bots, and The Weather Channel.

It is a great example for us to start talking about environmental data.

2.0.1 Newspaper - Los Angeles Times

Examine Figure 2.1 as a prototypical environmental data visualization from the LA Times.
